# Fleet Operations KPI Definitions

These KPIs model the core performance metrics used in fleet management and transportation analytics.

### Preventive Maintenance (PM) Compliance
Percentage of vehicles with PM completed on time during the selected period.
Formula: (Completed PM Jobs / Scheduled PM Jobs) * 100

### Average Repair Cost per Vehicle
Total repair spend divided by distinct vehicle count.
Formula: SUM(RepairCost) / DISTINCTCOUNT(VehicleID)

### Utilization Rate
Average daily usage measured in miles or hours.
Formula: AVERAGE(Utilization) / Time Period

### Cost per Mile
Total repair and maintenance cost divided by total miles traveled.
Formula: SUM(RepairCost) / SUM(Miles)
